# Walkthrough - Antigravity Autonomous Architect (AAA) Platform

The **Antigravity Meta-Architect (AMA)** has successfully initialized the AAA ecosystem. This production-grade platform serves as the central orchestration hub for transmuting intent into infrastructure.

## Changes Made

### 1. Foundation & Design System
- **Next.js 15 & React 19**: Initialized the project with the latest stack for optimal performance and forward-compatibility.
- **Midnight Luxe CSS**: Implemented a custom design system in [globals.css](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/app/globals.css) featuring:
    - **Deep Overlay Gradients**: Radial glows representing "Aura" and "Gravity".
    - **Glassmorphism**: High-blur utility classes (`.glass`) for premium UI depth.
    - **Neon Tokens**: CSS variables for electric primary and accent colors.

### 2. High-Fidelity Components
I have constructed the primary interface layers:
- **[Navbar](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx)**: Sticky glassmorphism header with Antigravity branding and responsive navigation.
- **[Hero Section](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/components/Hero.tsx)**: Cinematic entry point with cascading text animations and an "Intent Expansion" visual cue.
- **[Agent Dashboard](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/components/AgentDashboard.tsx)**: State-driven visualization of [Dev, Designer, DevOps] sub-agents with live progress monitoring and heartbeat animations.
- **[Terminal Simulator](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/components/Terminal.tsx)**: A monospaced log thread that simulates the real-time architectural synthesis process of the AMA.

### 3. Logic & Utilities
- **[cn Utility](file:///C:/Users/hlim/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/src/lib/utils.ts)**: Implementation of `clsx` and `tailwind-merge` for robust conditional styling.
- **Asset Integration**: Mapped Lucide-React icons and Framer Motion transitions across all interactions.

